OL,3,CWhy a Wirral landmark is taking a trip
OL,4,Cfrom Port Sunlight to London
OL,6,FA landmark in Wirral's historic soap
OL,7,Ffactory village is being sent to
OL,8,FLondon...to be cleaned.
OL,10,FPicturesque Port Sunlight was built to
OL,11,Fhouse workers at William Lever's
OL,12,FSunlight soap products factory back in
OL,13,F1888. The company was the forerunner
OL,14,Fto global giant Unilever.
OL,16,FIt's now Grade 2 listed and considered
OL,17,Fone of the finest examples of planned
OL,18,Findustrial settlements in the world.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
