OL,3,CWhy a Wirral landmark is taking a trip
OL,4,Cfrom Port Sunlight to London
OL,6,FBut it's boating pond is in need of
OL,7,Frepair and ugrade and the statue at
OL,8,Fits centre has been removed and taken
OL,9,Fto the capital for specialist
OL,10,Frestoration, that simple soap products
OL,11,Fcouldn't do!
OL,13,FIt is the first time the 'Sea Piece'
OL,14,Fsculpture has been removed since it
OL,15,Fwas installed in 1950
OL,17,Fby its creator, Sir Charles Wheeler,
OL,18,Fwho is most famous for his sculptures
OL,19,Fin London's
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
