OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772780660
OL,3,CWhy a Wirral landmark is taking a trip
OL,4,Cfrom Port Sunlight to London
OL,6,FTrafalgar Square and at the Bank of
OL,7,FEngland.
OL,9,FThe work's been commissioned by Port
OL,10,FSunlight Village Trust, the
OL,11,Findependent charity responsible for
OL,12,Fpreserving and promoting the Wirral
OL,13,Fvillage.
OL,15,FIt's partly funded by Lord
OL,16,FLeverhulme's Charitable Trust, but the
OL,17,Ftrust is appealing for public
OL,18,Fdonations to make all the improvements
OL,19,Fneeded for the Boating Pond.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
