OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772780660
OL,3,CWhy a Wirral landmark is taking a trip
OL,4,Cfrom Port Sunlight to London
OL,6,FIn 2021, it was discovered that the
OL,7,FBoating Pond required significant
OL,8,Fstructural work and so
OL,10,Fthe fountain was switched off and the
OL,11,Fpond emptied. Now, five years later,
OL,12,Fthe relocation of
OL,14,Fthe 'Sea Piece' sculpture will enable
OL,15,Fessential works to begin on
OL,16,Freconstructing the Boating
OL,18,FPond's basin and reintroduce the water
OL,19,Ffeature.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
