OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772780660
OL,3,CWhy a Wirral landmark is taking a trip
OL,4,Cfrom Port Sunlight to London
OL,6,FOnce the sculpture reaches a
OL,7,Fspecialist conservation studio in
OL,8,FLondon, with the support of
OL,10,Fconservators Rupert Harris
OL,11,FConservation and art-handlers Mtec, it
OL,12,Fwill undergo detailed
OL,14,Fassessment, cleaning and treatment.
OL,15,FIts modern brown patina will be
OL,16,Fremoved, and
OL,18,Fconservators will restore the
OL,19,Fsculpture as closely as possible to
OL,20,FSir Charles Wheeler's
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
