OL,3,CWhy a Wirral landmark is taking a trip
OL,4,Cfrom Port Sunlight to London
OL,6,Foriginal light green finish.
OL,8,FThe sculpture will return to Port
OL,9,FSunlight later this year.
OL,11,FAndrew Bowden, Chair of the Board of
OL,12,FTrustees, said: "Our project to renew
OL,13,Fthe Boating
OL,15,FPond reflects our commitment to
OL,16,Fpreserving the heritage and character
OL,17,Fof Port Sunlight while
OL,19,Fensuring that the village continues to
OL,20,Fthrive for future residents and
OL,21,Fvisitors. We are grateful
OL,26,@tD@QOU
