OL,3,CWhy a Wirral landmark is taking a trip
OL,4,Cfrom Port Sunlight to London
OL,6,Ffor the community's patience and
OL,7,Fsupport as we carry out this essential
OL,8,Fwork, and to the
OL,10,FLord Leverhulme's Charitable Trust for
OL,11,Ftheir support in making this project
OL,12,Fhappen `
OL,14,Fhowever we need everyone's further
OL,15,Fsupport to ensure we can complete this
OL,16,Fimportant work
OL,18,Fand we would welcome any donations,
OL,19,Fbig or small."
