OL,3,CWhy a Wirral landmark is taking a trip
OL,4,Cfrom Port Sunlight to London
OL,6,FJean Milton, Director of Heritage at
OL,7,FPort Sunlight Village Trust, said:
OL,8,F"Sea Piece is an
OL,10,Ficonic and muchloved landmark in Port
OL,11,FSunlight's landscape, and its
OL,12,Fconservation marks a
OL,14,Fsignificant milestone for the village.
OL,15,FThis phase of the project is the
OL,16,Fresult of extensive
OL,18,Fplanning, and we are pleased to be
OL,19,Fworking with highly respected
OL,20,Fspecialists to ensure the
OL,26,@pD@AOU
