OL,3,CWhy a Wirral landmark is taking a trip
OL,4,Cfrom Port Sunlight to London
OL,6,Fsculpture receives the highest
OL,7,Fstandard of care. The work we are
OL,8,Fundertaking now will
OL,10,Fsafeguard both the sculpture and the
OL,11,FBoating Pond for generations to come."
OL,13,FIn the coming weeks, hoardings will be
OL,14,Finstalled around the monument to allow
OL,15,Fstructural
OL,17,Fworks on the pond basin to begin. Port
OL,18,FSunlight Village Trust hopes the work
OL,19,Fwill completed
